snippet.title: Johnny Depp 'threw champagne bottle at Amber' before 'dragging her by hair'
snippet.description: threw a magnum of champagne at Amber Heard when they got into a fight on her birthday, the High Court heard today.  The Pirates of the Carribbean actor is accused of getting angry when Heard confronted him about arriving late to her birthday celebrations on April 22 2016 and leaving early  Sasha Wass QC asked Depp if he picked up the large bottle of champagne and threw it at Heard which missed her, before dragging her to the floor by her hair.   Depp is in the fourth day of his libel case against News Group Newspapers and giving testimony and denies the egations.   He said he missed the start of the party because he had some bad news and "may have" smoked some marijuana "to calm down".    Depp said Heard was very upset he was so late and "she became very upset, very angry."  The lawyer told him: "You took Amber's anger about you being late as criticism, and you don't like criticism... This provoked you to become angry"  "And you were, at the time you were angry, near a magnum bottle  ...
